  "description": "[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;20px&#8221;][vc_row_inner content_width=&#8221;grid&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text] OUR PRACTICE Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm is a specialized boutique law firm located in the heart of Fresno, CA. Our firm is equipped with aggressive trial lawyers who have been collectively practicing for over 50 years. The best way to describe us is by having GRIT: goal-oriented resilient intuitive trustworthy We represent all types of clients and we will give you the time and respect that you deserve. We handle all of our legal matters with the utmost integrity, honesty, compassion, professionalism, and personal attention to detail.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8376&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;60&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row..."
